data.description: Location, location! West Asheville close to dining, shopping & entertainment.  New carpets and appliances. Wood flooring in living room. New front door, 3 bedroom with 2 and a half bathrooms, off street parking. Situated far off the street. All bedrooms upstairs. Large Primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom and sliding glass door on to private deck and large closet.
